<style>
  :root {
    --deep-teal: #006d77; /* Deep teal */
    --rich-gold: #ffc107; /* Rich gold for hover effects */
    --dark-gold: #e6a700; /* Slightly darker gold */
    --light-gray: #f7f7f7; /* Light gray for background */
    --dark-gray: #333333; /* Dark gray for text */
    --white: #ffffff; /* Standard white */
    --footer-gray: #343a40; /* Subtle footer gray */
  }

  body {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    background: var(--light-gray); /* Light gray background */
  }

  .policy-container {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--light-gray); /* Use light gray for container */
  }

  .policy-header {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--deep-teal); /* Use deep teal for header */
    color: var(--white); /* Use white text */
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .policy-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-content {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .policy-content h2 {
    color: var(--deep-teal); /* Deep teal for subheadings */
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .policy-content ul {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  .policy-content ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--dark-gray); /* Dark gray for readability */
  }

  .policy-content a {
    color: var(--deep-teal); /* Teal for links */
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .policy-content a:hover {
    color: var(--rich-gold); /* Gold for hover effect */
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
<%layout("/layouts/boilerplate.ejs")-%>
<body>
  <main class="policy-container">
    <section class="policy-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>
        Your privacy is important to us. At DreamDwell, we are committed to
        protecting your personal information and ensuring transparency in how we
        collect, use, and safeguard your data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-content">
      <h2>What Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Personal information, such as your name, email address, and contact
          details, when you sign up or interact with our services.
        </li>
        <li>
          Location data to tailor property listings based on your preferences.
        </li>
        <li>
          Technical data like IP address, browser type, and device information
          for improving user experience.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          To provide and personalize our services, such as recommending relevant
          listings.
        </li>
        <li>To communicate with you about updates, offers, or promotions.</li>
        <li>To maintain the security and integrity of our platform.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal
        information at any time. For assistance, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@dreamdwell.com">support@dreamdwell.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We use industry-standard measures to protect your data. However, no
        method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we
        cannot guarantee absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected
        on this page, and we encourage you to review our privacy policy
        periodically.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
